    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit boasts a 8,400 RPM redline, facilitated by eight individual throttle bodies and a sophisticated ionic current knock sensing system. Power is delivered via a 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission to a variable M-differential lock with a 3.15 final drive ratio. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and retains its original carbon fiber roof to optimize the center of gravity. Meticulously maintained, this example features documented preventative rod bearing replacement using VAC coated shells and upgraded throttle actuators. The factory Alpine White paint shows zero track wear, and the undercarriage remains concours-level clean.",
      "price": 46500.0,
